---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<MainLayout title="Services"> 
   <Breadcrumb title="Services" />
 <section id="main-container" class="main-container">
  <div class="container">
<div class="row">

      <div class="col-xl-3 col-lg-4">
        <div class="sidebar sidebar-left">
          <div class="widget">
            <h3 class="widget-title">Services</h3>
            <ul class="nav service-menu">
              <li><a href={ baseUrl + "services_mobile"}>Mobile Vehicle Service & Maintenance</a></li>
              <li><a href={ baseUrl + "services_auto"}>Auto Electrician Services</a></li>
              <li class="active"><a href={ baseUrl + "services_air"}>Automotive Air Conditioning Regas & Maintenance</a></li> 
            </ul>
          </div>   
        </div><!-- Sidebar end -->
      </div><!-- Sidebar Col end -->

      <div class="col-xl-8 col-lg-8">
        <div class="content-inner-page">

          <h2 class="column-title mrt-0">Automotive Air Conditioning Regas & Maintenance</h2>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 text-justify">
              <p>Your vehicle’s air conditioning system plays an important role in maintaining <b>driver comfort and visibility</b>, especially during hot and humid conditions. Over time, air conditioning systems can lose refrigerant, develop leaks, or suffer from component wear that reduces cooling performance.
                Our automotive air conditioning regas and maintenance service provides professional inspection, diagnosis, and servicing to ensure your system continues to operate efficiently and reliably.
                Using specialised air conditioning servicing equipment, we check system pressures, inspect components, and safely recharge the refrigerant to restore optimal cooling performance.
              </p>
              <p><b>Our automotive air conditioning regas and maintenance service</b> provides professional inspection, diagnosis, and servicing to ensure your system continues to operate efficiently and reliably.</p>
              <p>Using specialised air conditioning servicing equipment, we check system pressures, inspect components, and safely recharge the refrigerant to restore optimal cooling performance.</p>
              <hr/> 
            </div><!-- col end -->
          </div><!-- 1st row end-->

          <div class="gap-40"></div>

          <div id="page-slider" class="page-slider">
            <div class="item">
              <img loading="lazy" class="img-fluid" src={ baseUrl + "assets/images/projects/project5.jpg" }alt="project-slider-image" />
            </div>

            <div class="item">
              <img loading="lazy" class="img-fluid" src={ baseUrl + "assets/images/projects/project6.jpg"} alt="project-slider-image" />
            </div>
          </div><!-- Page slider end -->

          <div class="gap-40"></div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <h5 class="text-primary">Air Conditioning Regas</h5>
              <p>Over time, refrigerant levels can decrease, reducing the efficiency of your air conditioning system. Our <b>air conditioning regas service</b> restores the correct refrigerant levels, improving cooling performance and overall system efficiency.</p>
              <h5 class="text-primary">System Inspection & Diagnostics</h5>
              
              <p>Before regassing the system, we perform a full system inspection to check for leaks, damaged components, or other issues that may affect performance.</p>

              <b>Our diagnostics include:</b>
              <ul class="list-arrow mb-2">
                <li>System pressure testing</li>
                <li>Leak detection</li>
                <li>Compressor performance checks</li>
                <li>Condenser and component inspection</li>
              </ul>
              <p>This ensures the system is operating correctly and prevents unnecessary refrigerant loss.</p>

              <h5 class="text-primary">Air Conditioning Maintenance</h5>
              <p>Routine air conditioning maintenance helps extend the life of your system and prevent costly repairs.</p>
              <b>Maintenance services include:</b>
              <ul class="list-arrow mb-2">
                <li>Cabin air filter inspection and replacement</li>
                <li>System cleaning and airflow checks</li>
                <li>Electrical system inspection</li>
                <li>Compressor and belt inspection</li>
              </ul>
              <p>Regular servicing ensures your air conditioning system remains efficient, reliable, and ready for year-round use.</p>
            </div>            
          </div>
          <!--2nd row end -->

          <div class="gap-40"></div>

         

        </div><!-- Content inner end -->
      </div><!-- Content Col end -->


    </div><!-- Main row end -->
  </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>